      "content": "i know about the helplines. they dont get it. they think there's a way back to how things were, but that's gone. that part of my life is just dead. everything i worked for, every single thing, just evaporated. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just this heavy realization that i'm a failure and there's no way to fix it. i'm already at the bottom... i might as well just stay here.",
