      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like everyone is just waiting for me to \"get better\" so life can go back to normal, but there is no normal anymore. even if i fix the money, the person i was is gone. i'm just a ghost walking around. it feels so much easier to just stop fighting the gravity and let it happen, you know? like, instead of fighting to stay afloat, why not just let go and find some actual peace?",
